Description_lang: Delivers a series of strikes so diabolical, it is unable to be described accurately in text. Affected targets will similarly be unlikely to have understood the full effect of this spell as its blinding brilliance washes over them like tidal wave of devastation.Inflicts $320142s1 Shadow damage to all enemies every $320141T1 sec for $320141D, increasing in damage by $320142s2%. This effect stacks.
